  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Reduces power cuts to one hour",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Chairman of Public Utility Commission Mr. Janaka Ratnayake said that due to the restoration of the first power generator of the Lakwijaya Power Plant in Norochchole and the addition of it to the national electricity system and the decrease in electricity demand, today (28) the power cut has been reduced to one hour and the one hour power cut will be implemented at night.",
        "Mr. Ratnayake further said that he will pay attention to the 300 megawatts from the first generator of the Lakwijaya Power Plant and decide on the electricity distribution next week."
      ],
